eautiful Bed Room Suite we are giving\ng away, and let us tell you all about how you can get it. See\nthe many specials we have for this sale.\nI Rhodes Furniture Co. 1\nWEST JEFFERSON, N. C. fi\n3* S\nTHE CHRISTMAS HARVEST\n(By Ateon Secor, in Successful\n1 i' 7. Farming)\nOLD SANTA CLAUSE\u2014\nSome don\u2019t believe in him because\nHe makes them spend\nThey like to borrow, but never lend\nThat Christmas cheer\nWhich permeates this .time of year.\nThey are tight-fisted cynics, these.\nThey never know how presents\nplease\nThe little kids, and others;\nThe sisters and the brothers;\nThe care-worn dads and weary\nmothers.\nThey never learned to live\nBecause they never learned to give.\nYou\u2019ve got to plant before you\nreap.\nIf all you keep\nYour soul gets barren, sterile, sour.\nIt takes the power\nOs cheerful giving\nTo give a zest to living.\nMr. Lawrence Campbell of Bald\nwin, Maryland, returned home\n'Monday morning.\u00bb He had attend\ned the funeral of Mr. Henry A\nCampbell.\nPAGE FIVE","height":"27609","width":"18870"}}
